<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-31-1062 </DOCNO><TEXT>We prove an existence-uniqueness result for the solution of a nonlinearfourth-order differential equation which determines the shape of a grainboundary groove forming by surface diffusion. A variational approximationof the problem leads to an efficient numerical method.</TEXT></DOC>